WEBVTT

00:00:01.083 --> 00:00:04.725
OK, as an attorney,
as a political commentator,

00:00:04.750 --> 00:00:07.500
and frankly, as a former
White House official,

00:00:07.917 --> 00:00:09.768
I used to think I knew a lot

00:00:09.792 --> 00:00:12.184
about how America picks a president.

00:00:12.208 --> 00:00:14.393
I was wrong, I did not know.

00:00:14.417 --> 00:00:15.684
And this year,

00:00:15.708 --> 00:00:18.434
I've been doing some research
into some of the fine print

00:00:18.458 --> 00:00:21.226
and all the different things
in our constitution

00:00:21.250 --> 00:00:22.643
that we never talk about,

00:00:22.667 --> 00:00:25.393
and I've discovered some legal loopholes

00:00:25.417 --> 00:00:26.893
that shocked me,

00:00:26.917 --> 00:00:28.684
I guarantee will shock you,

00:00:28.708 --> 00:00:30.976
and could determine the way